value: Це все, що в тебе є?
This is the part I like!
У мене для тебе дещо є!
Machine blood. Do not fall in.
Machine blood. Tastes bad, but is very filling.
[Grunt] Is not nice. Do not touch.
That slime does not belong here, I think.
[Grunt] Slime. I do not like slime.
Dark ahead. I hunt better in the dark.
Never any light in these places...
Do not need light. Just follow nose.
Scariest thing in the darkness is me, yes?
I told ya to stay with me!
У мене для тебе дещо є!
А ось і коробка з бабахом!
This rock is a friendly one!
When fighting starts, Spark ‘Ead, you stay behind me.
Kind? No! Do not want you getting in the way. Not kind! Tough!
Ти мені подобаєшся. Говориш мало. Б'єшся багато.
See? I am in awe! You are true Ogryn!
Не проблема! Тепер моя черга, так?
Knew a poem once. Think it went: Raaaararrrrgggh!
Me too! Only ... would not fit. Is not fair.
Yes. From long line of lummoxes. Have pedigree.
Am Ogryn of hidden depths. Everybody says so.
Я завжди насторожі. Ніщо не пройде повз мене.
Я не підведу тебе, Іскро-Башка. Ось побачиш!
You should stick with me, Spark 'Ead. I have much to teach you.
I am very impressive, yes? Would be more so with proper armour.
Maybe I hollow out tank and wear that?
I can take it! I will show you!
At which side? Left side or ... other left side?
Aha! Am understanding now. Thank you.
I am glad Emperor is with us ... he is with us, yes?
Ah ... Will be more careful. Would not want to step on him.
Was thinking this too, but nothing will change.
Still not sure what this comm bead is for.
Ah! Metalface is in my head again ... How does she do that?
No ... Voice was in my head. Cannot fool me!
Yes. I am "a right one". Sergeant told me so.
Heretics should run, yes? We always win.
Yes. Is very sad. I am glad I am not like that. You could learn that from me.
Still here! Going to crush them all!
Why bother? I will win. I always win.
Bah! I am sanest person I know.
Not sure how you get "life". "Death" is very simple: hit something hard? Death.
Not sure what that means, but all right.
Wish I could do what you do, Spark 'Ead. Looks fun!
Maybe if I think hard enough, I could do it too?
No, Shouty was right - there are heretics everywhere!
Try to keep up, Spark 'Ead! You will miss all the fun.
Ah, but then I would miss you, Spark 'Ead. However the Hounds coming up behind would not ...
Am easily pleased. Just want friends, food and things to kill.
I admit nothing. Am famously gnomic.
Could be. Not very good with words.
This is the life, eh Boss?
I hear you, Boss. Don't worry, your secret is safe with me.
Ненавиджу єретиків. Вони тільки те й роблять, що вбивають... Звичайно, ми теж вбиваємо, але вони на це заслуговують, так?
I cannot hear them. Perhaps it is all the shooting?
How did you fit them all in there?
You are tough, Spark 'Ead. Might make you honourary Ogryn.
Of course you do, Spark 'Ead. I am the best.
Perhaps I should make you honourary Ogryn? I will talk to the others.
Very important rule of battle: do not get killed!
Do not get cocky. You could get killed at any time.
Cannot remember how many missions I've been on.
Maybe the two are linked. More missions: more impressive?
First rule of battle: kill them first!
Them. You know ... all of them!
Why would I? No one is as handsome as me.
Feel sorry for everyone who needs him. You know ... ugly people.
Shouty uses many big words. I would like to learn big words. Become more "som-nam-bu-list".
Is true. Am often very "pen-ta-tonic". Will you teach me, Shouty?
Ми заблукали? Майже впевнений, що заблукали.
Він завжди слухає. Не має чим зайнятися?
Yes! Cannot say the same for everything else, which is often in wrong place.
We make a good team, Shouty.
I am strong, tough, cunning, fearless ... and you? You make funny noises. Make enemy laugh so I can kill them.
Very good. And very messy. And it smells bad.
Am in bad mood. Want to smash something.
You make good point. I feel better already.
No! Only gunfire and screaming. Is very soothing.
Do not fear. If I hear it, I will tell you!
So long since I saw Grendyl. Might be dead.
I too would like to fade into mystery.
Often do not feel them, that is problem. Morrow says "I have no sense, so have no feeling".
Yes, I said so too. Did not look happy. I think he is very bitter man.
Не забувай дивитися на мене постійно. Я дуже на-в-чаль-ний.
Will be sure to make lots of noise so you know where I am.
Wish I had a pet. Something to talk to and hug.
Yes ... Yes. And be fed tasty treats, like broiled dog's liver.
No worries. Stay close. I will kill all the Dregs!
Oh! I thought you were hitting me on purpose.
Very good of you. Am grateful.
I wish it was quiet. I think better when is quiet.
No. No, no. Have to think out loud, otherwise is not real.
Not sure. Would need to think about it.
Have very big, strong thoughts because Ogryn is big and strong.
Don't know. Will give it serious thought.
True. Do not know the meaning of the word "surr-en-der". Cannot spell it either. Is great shame.
Almost none. Always put too many Rs in RRRraaaaarrrggggh!
No, but heretics are very stinky.
Of course I do. You are much smaller than me.
Good. Do not like talking to dead.
Even worse when they talk back.
I would never taunt you, Spark 'Ead. Do not have the smarts.
No. Am right here ... Are your eyes working properly?
Ogryns are best. Everybody knows this!
That is because we are the best.
You see? I win ... Which means I am the best.
Good, thinking is very important. You should do more of it.
You see? Already you are learning to follow my advice. That is the benefit of thought.
I like you, Shouty. You are very angry.
Hey! I am not ... One of those long, complicated words.
You have deep, booming voice. Almost like Ogryn!
Звісно. Я Оґрин. Хіба ти не знав? [Сміх]
I like it on Atoma. There is always something to do.
Yes. Always there are more. Like bugs.
And go "squish" when you stomp them. Is fun.
Yes, I am very big. And very impressive, no?
Sorry! I will try ducking more. That might help.
I am. Everybody says so ... Wait, what does "canny" mean?
What prize? I should have prize. After all, I am canny.
SORRY. CANNOT HEAR. THINK I MIGHT BE DEAF ... No. Wait. Had shrapnel in ear. That's better.
Why do you hate Spark 'Eads so much, Shouty?
Why not change creed to say they are nice?
Okay. I go do that. Which way is Terra?
I like you, little ones. You are family.
Tiny, squishy family that smells strange and uses long words. But still family.
So. Here we are again, yes?
I like you. You are Ogryn of few words.
What do you mean? Everywhere is fire zone.
Ah, so it is you who keeps shooting me in the back? Stop it!
No, no, no. I say "are we friends?" and you say "You are my best friend". Otherwise I am sad.
Not so! You are shooting the wrong people. Obvious!
No! You stop shooting me in the back!
Oi, Shouty! Do you love Emperor?
Where? I will kill them all, so Emperor loves me even more!
Everyone likes me. Is Ogryn musk you see. Very powerful.
Yes, is true! I am irresistable to all. Even metal birds.
Is no problem. You are very small and delicate. Need Ogryn to stop you getting hurt.
Want to read. Cannot. Is very sad.
How they do that if so tiny ... No, wait. I see.
You always seem angry. Are you sleeping enough?
Does not sound good. No sleep. No dreams.
No breakfast, yes. That is very bad.
No take-backs. I am smart, you are ... what I said. And both of us friends, yes?
I have much to say. And people like it when I talk.
Don't know. Don't care. If everyone is happy, where is the harm?
Yes, and I kill people for Emperor too!
No. It means I kill twice as many. Is why Emperor loves me more than you.
Nothing can. I am too strong. Have im-penny-trable "Force of Will".
Spark 'Eads are very wise. Know many big words. I like.
Air smells strange. Like old boots and dead scav-rats.
Nasty smell, everywhere we go. Do not like.
You put it very well, Pal. I am impressed.
Wonder if Morrow will let me have war dog? Fetch. Stay. Kill! Good times.
Might ask Morrow if I can have dog.
Eat them anyway! Does not kill, makes stronger, yes?
Bit of rot adds flavour, yes?
Do not know what you mean. I can see perfectly. Long as it's close.
Can see things when they are in thumping range. Good enough.
I agree! Also, I am bigger and stronger than them!
Yes! We have nothing to fear!
I think you are trying to trick me, but I won't fall for it!
You tell them, Boss! You and me, we know the truth.
I am ready for anything! Is my best feature!
Follow me! I know the way ... I think.
Have to feel our way forward. If it squishes, kill it!
How I am I supposed to hear over all this talking?
[Dog-like Howl] Do not worry friends, that was me. Was good joke, yes?
Stay behind me, comrades. Safest place.
Hit them in head. Crack like Grox egg.
Have one job. Do as told.
We also crush heretic, no? Two jobs.
You think Emperor pleased with me?
Do not worry friends, I protect.
I break heretics in half, yes?
Do not be scared, little comrades. I am here.
This is life, yes? Fighting with friends!
Me, afraid? Fear is for little people.
When do we get bigger guns?
Bad things lurk in dark. Like me.
These heretics crazy to mess with me …
If they kill you, friends, I kill them back. Promise.
Be a shame. Will need new friends.
I like part when I shoot and they fall down.
Squishy. Do not like the squish.
Yes, and smell even worse than you.
Give it name, too. Hug it. This is important.
Big Boss clever. Know what he is doing, yes?
Ha! What did he say to that?
Patience, small one. Fight come soon.
They will regret finding me, yes.
You have me to protect you now.
They mess with you again, I pull off heads, yes?
Do not worry, comrade. I am here.
I never fall ... but then, I never weak.
I never fall ... but then, I never weak.
Fire many bullets, target gets hit. Good strategy.
Surely the dead cannot feel shame?
Sometimes, I like to make it slow...
Rather show them might of big Ogryn!
Too grogging quiet! Need a bigger fight!
This is a good day. Much fighting!
Stay close! Ogryn keep you safe!
Much killing to be done, yes?
Why you all look so gloomy? Smile!
We fight as team, we win! Simple!
Do not fear! Ogryn stands with you!
Is it insult? Better not be insult.
Aiming such a little gun is hard.
Spray and pray. It is the only way.
Many bullets. Many dead. Good times.
Will not do it again. I promise!
You speak of fighting spirit, yes?
Life is too short to worry!
I am not afraid! Stay behind me!
Might ask Big Boss to make me Bone 'Ead. Be smart, yes?
Want to be Bone 'Ead. Think better. Smarter!
Gotta think more. Need Bone 'Ead upgrade.
Was thinking the same! Fight you for it!
Let's find something to kill, yes?
Yes! Next time bring Thudd Gun or Battle Cannon!
I have good feeling about this mission.
Mission is going well. Maybe big reward at end, yes?
Yes! Feeling very good about this.
You ever pull head off heretic? Nothing better!
Grow muscle, stay warm. Is good advice.
I am warm. I am always warm.
I would make good enforcer, yes?
Stick with me, comrades. Ogryn protect!
They want to be avenged, yes?
There is wisdom in the dead. You should listen.
No Ogryn had more medals than he!
Do not worry, Ogryn will protect.
No fret, Shouty. Ogryn stands ready.
Problem with grenades is they are too small.
Fight to the end, for Emperor!
I like dreams. All that blood...
Dreams are always angry. And loud.
Keep clear head. You will fight better!
Not good to fight drunk. Fall over too much.
Emperor is good and strong. We be strong too.
No way, Boss! Ogryns always win.
Means there are plenty to kill, yes?
At least we will not be bored!
Fire good. Kills and cooks. Yum.
I write orders down. Sadly, cannot read.
I never forget. We here to kill!
If it stay down, it good, yes?
Can never tell if food is bad until it come back out.
Used it on that little wound?
Ah. Did not think. Will do better next time.
You know "The Ratling's Bloomers", yes? I will start.
Why not? I am just getting warmed up!
I think I should be in charge.
Been thinking. Better if I leader, yes?
Ogryn born leader. You follow. Obey.
Is good idea! I claim co-leader!
Not food. Not ammo. No good.
This saint... She live here, yes?
I would like to see that.
Be of good cheer, Spark 'Ead! I am your friend.
Loosen up, Spark 'Ead. All is well.
You do know that the city's not alive, Boss?
Never mind, Boss. We'll fix her up.
I am bigger than you lot. Should have bigger gun.
I am strong. Strong enough to carry bigger gun!
I deserve bigger gun. Cannon, perhaps? Yes!
No! I get bigger gun first! I call dibs!
Bigger gun. More boom. More fun!
Goes up, yes. Goes down, yes. Sometimes goes down hard. Splat. Not good.
Stairs do not collapse under feet. Well ... not often.
Do I get medal? I hope it is medal.
We get reward now, or later?
I thank him for making me strongest!
Yes! Me! I am always first.
Food is food. Do not overthink, yes?
Maybe I examine your brain too. With shovel!
Hrn. Perhaps I look in your head, yes?
You think I'm dumb, don't you?
You think I'm stupid? I see it in your eyes.
Not stupid. Am not. Whatever you think.
You just as smart as me!
All of us dead by then.
Will not live to see it.
Would not say no to a little peace and quiet.
Not a good time for that.
I am not tired. I am unstoppable.
Sleep is for the weak. Hah!
Sorry! I think quieter in future.
Legs always tired. Would rather drive tank.
Want thicker armour. Maybe drive tank, yes?
Armour good. Tank better. Should drive tank.
Sounds good. But Big Boss will say no.
This place? Then I am honoured!
I get two medals for saving this place, no?
As long as they die, who cares?
They are mad. All of them!
Never mind! You're among friends now!
Sad story. Kill something. That will cheer you up.
Happy to help, for a finder's fee.
As long as you remember your friends, yes?
I trust strong arm and big gun!
Come, let us all be friends, yes?
Yes! We be heroes! Have statues ... Medals.
What are we waiting for? Victory today, yes?
Tried to clean weapon. It broke.
I am good soldier. Nothing to say.
You will be fine. Trust Ogryn.
We done somethin' to offend you?
Ain't good enough for your company?
Big world. Gonna need lotsa warriors to take it back.
Don't need help. We've got this.
Don't matter. Show me what to hit. I'll hit them.
Recon Valkyrie came in today. On fire. Crew screaming. Mad. What happened to 'em?
It’s almost as tough as me!
I have idea! Shoot it from behind!
Always a sound plan! I approve!
Never knew true home. Was taken.
Hrrn. Never knock the pilot. Unless you want to crash.
Trust pilot, or crash. Simple choice.
Pilot's a good fighter. Knows how to stand.
Aim at the head! Blow brains out!
Not our business. Not our problem.
He's the Big Boss. Nothing else matters.
Big Boss sounds unhappy. Looks worse.
Troubled and angry. Bad news for us.
Tertium's lost. He knows it. All else is ... hope.
He hears that? Be even less happy.
Don't tell him that. Won't go well.
Morrow was running missions for the Biggest Boss?
Heard that Morrow was at Hades Hive on Armageddon. Doesn't look that old.
Morrow fought in the Second War for Armageddon. Hah. Isn't old enough!
Too tough to die, maybe? Good.
No end to battles ... And that's good!
Ogryn fight for Emperor. Maybe become saint if fight hard enough?
Emperor greatest hero. Very strong. Good drinker. Yes?
Shouty uses strange words. Wondering why.
Groggin' dregs… Got a lucky shot…
No more noise from that Rager!
Tough little man. Not so tough as ogryn. Feel bad for him.
Don't worry, little friend! I still like you more!
Very unkind. They were trying to help.
Did not feel pain. Very strange.
Ain't that strong, are ya Mutie?
Не така вже й велика, чи не так, Мутяка?
Be of good cheer! Trapper is done!
Did we kill the Trapper? Good!
Guess we let him off, yeah?
You can relax. I am here. Everything will be fine!
Not so tough now, are ya?
This is how it is done!
Quicker to break gate down, no?
This one almost as tough as Ogryn!
It was strong. I was stronger.
This is what skulls eat, no?
They are all so eager to die!
Don't ya know how to shoot straight?
Yer shooting the wrong guy, Psyker!
Stop it! Yer shootin' me, Psyker!
Oi! That hit me, ya blockhead.
I'm tough, but I'm not so tough I like being shot!
Want me to shoot ya back, Zealot?
Give it a rest, Zealot! You shot me!
Big mouth, small brain, bad aim!
We go down, we stay there!
See that switch? What's it do?
This device, it does not work.
Maybe someone else should try, no?
Listen, scanner, I will break you!
What's that? I don't like it…
Got a fight on our hands!
Perhaps I can keep one as a pet, yes?
No Hound can keep me pinned!
Stay behind me! I will protect you!
Hah! Success will soon be ours!
I get to do the next one!

Strange life. Not part of the Astra Mili … Astra Miliata… Not part of the Imperial Guard no more, not after things went bad on Komlar. Funny, really. Ogryns kept fighting long after the little ones ran away. Held that hill for three days. Little men in spiky armour charged us again and again. We broke them and threw them onto the rocks. Three days we held alone, but there were no medals. No food. Only big, angry words.
Oi! Forget about me, did you?
Not to worry, Pal. Happens to all of us.
Up. Down. Up. Down. What's wrong with you, Pal?
Oh, come on! OgrynS don't fall over!
Psyker! All those brains, doesn't know how to stand.
Look at the Veteran. Always fallin' down.
Can't ya stay on yer feet, Shouty?
Reckon I took a wrong turn…
No one say a groggin' word…
Lotsa hidey holes. Watch for ambush.
Horrible stuff. Should burn it out.
Security station was abandoned, not overrun.
Don't like this place. Eyes sharp.
There is more than one type of Ogryn, yes? We are special.
Many kinds of Ogryn. You lucky you get me.
Many kinds of Ogryn. Not all as friendly as me.
Only three matter. Strong, stronger, strongest!
Only matter of time till we take charge, yes?
I am Alpha type! No doubt.
Alpha type, yes? That must be me!
Very tiny, no? Fit in pocket!
Really hairy feet. Is strange, no?
Stunty little runts, but very big feet, no?
Ogryn is only abhuman that matter.
This abhuman will do duty, you will see!
Hmm, a good question. Umm... What it mean?
Ogryn have big soul. That is end of it.
If Ogryn have soul, it is biggest and best!
What I miss most about Guard is tanks!
Used to have tank support. Not any more.
In old days, we have tank support. Flatten this place!
Battle tanks. That is what we need.
Is good idea. Somebody should ask Boss.
Only if I get to drive, yes?
Once saw a Leman Russ Punisher tank turn whole squad to goo. Nasty.
Battlecannon is best! Or maybe Punisher cannon. Hmm...
I fought in Auxilia. Proud Ogryns. Strong Ogryns!
Remember charge of Ogryns. Smell of enemy blood. Good days!
У Гвардії дають більше медалей. Мені подобається Гвардія.
На мене багато кричали. Але воювати було добре!
Оґрин не боїться комісара. Оґрин виконує накази.
Оґрин завжди виконує накази. Комісару подобається це.
Завжди робіть те, що вам кажуть. Це найкращий спосіб.
Роби, що сказано. Отримуй медаль. Все просто.
Вони розповідають чудові історії про Імператора!
I remember. Shouties make us proud.
Better class of Shouty in Auxilia...
I think ship's captain is pirate.
They say Rogue Trader is same as pirate.
Rogue Trader is… space pirate, yes?
Is true our captain was pirate?
Compared to Big Boss, she is cheery!
I think she want her ship back, no?
Вона не така вже і погана.
So many people to boss about…
Should have Ogryn in charge instead.
Stay out of her way, yes?
You are afraid of xenos, yes?
I think she is pirate. Sounds fun.
Why all heretics we meet so... gooey?
What is wrong with heretics on Atoma? Why they all sick and gooey?
Heretics we fight all have plague, yes? Why?
What is with plague-heretics? Why they like goo so much?
I think they pray to the goo. Strange, no?
They worship goo like god. Disgusting.
Ogryn never get sick. Ogryn strong!
Lucky I am healthy as grox! [Sniff. Cough]
God, monster, alien. Tell me fight it, I fight.
Emperor is only god. Big boss say so.
Why we always fight the gooey god? Is disgusting, no?
This is where daemons live? Makes sense.
And you think this is where daemons live, yes?
I do not understand anything you said.
It does not good to talk like this. Try being quiet.
Heretic Space Marine? Do not believe it!
But... Space Marine is hero, no?
This is bad news. Do not care for it.
I hear of thing called "Eye of Terror". What this?
Crew of Mourningstar talk of Eye of Terror. What is it?
I hear much of this Eye of Terror... What is it?
I hear only bad things about Eye of Terror.
I never see these Daemons. You sure they exist?
Maybe we take extra care... Just in case.
Do not like sound of this.
Do not like sound of this.
Do not worry, I protect you from Daemon.
Lion's Gate? Do not know it.
Hope they had Ogryns to help out.
Ha! Daemons lose, yes? Good story.
When you speak of Emperor, you call him a god, yes?
So Emperor is god? Strange, no?
We call him Sky-God. He live in sky.
They say he hear us all the time. He hear us now!
Pity he is not Ogryn god. But nobody is perfect.
It is good we have god on our side. Means we will win!
I like how they kill things with fire!
They are shouty ones with flamers, yes?
Do not need army when have Ogryn!
I do not like change. Am happy with team.
Have them in Auxilia. Shout a lot.
Bet there are no Ogryn Missionaries, no?
They serve Emperor, they must be okay.
Would like to meet Missionary. Sound interesting.
Do not know who they are, but like sound of it!
If Emperor like Synod, I like Synod, yes?
I would prefer psalm. Good sing-song, yes?
Make sure they get name right on medal, yes.
If Ogryn not mutant, who is?
How you tell who is mutant?
Mutant is bad, yes? What are they?
They can have three arms, eh? Would be funny...
I hear mutants have head of fly, or extra legs.
Find mutant, kill mutant. But not our mutant. Got it.
Confusing. You just say who to kill, yes?
Best way to get answers is punch in face, yes?
Innocence proves nothing. Heard Big Boss say so.
Put fear in them, they behave. Simple.
Change vox-tape, Shouty. Heard this one before.
How to tell good Spark-Ead from bad one?
If you see one, point them out, yes.
Best way to fight psyker: Keep head empty.
Explain to me this Indomitus Crusade, yes?
Indomitus Crusade is good thing, no?
What is happening with Indomitus Crusade?
Big war, fought by big man in blue, yes?
Biggest war ever, all across space. Good times!
Heroes of Imperium are best heroes!
Is that why I got headache?
I am awake enough already, comrade.
This talk does not help us.
Do not understand any of what you say.
Big scar in space. Very bad.
I hear big war happen in Dark Imperium.
We fight good fight, yes? Chin up!
Take heart, friends! We fight for Emperor, yes?
So many, all led by Grendyl.
Hope there is room to sleep.
We are bottom of pile, yes?
Do as you're told, life is simpler.
That is why Grendyl is Biggest Boss.
Do not need faith. Just orders.
I like Metalface. Gives clear orders.
Metalface is my favourite. Orders are clear, no?
Know where you stand with Tech-Lady.
Prefer Metalface's orders to Big Boss.
Those noises she makes… They are words?
Ah, you don't understand. It's fine.
Do not think Metalface likes us much.
A strange one. But useful, no?
There are worse than her on Atoma.
She make guns work good. I like her.
So… You know what I am thinking right now?
Ha! You will find nothing in my head.
You find anything good or not?
Must be boring to live so long.
The purser is hiring bodyguards. Might apply.
Purser is looking for new bodyguards? Might apply.
Purser is hiring guards. Think I should try?
Purser need guard for stores. Might apply.
Pah! You are just too small for job, no?
Would be nice to be appreciated, no?
You say nice things. Maybe I stay.
Suppose you need me to protect you, yes?
Would like to wrestle that one!
I wrestle her for it, yes?
Heard she once beat Ogryn in fight!
I want to be her friend.
All scum live at bottom of hive. So who live higher up?
Top of hive is pointy bit. Who live there?
Anybody live at top of hive?
I think Governor must live there, no?
Bosses up top, grunts at bottom. Just like Guard.
Do not think we will see spire. Oh well.
You say word, I tear gangers to pieces!
You want me kill gangers, I kill gangers. No problem!
They not worse things we meet in here.
I will protect you from gangs.
Just stay clear of sump. Bad things down there. Very bad.
Too crowded for Ogryn. Could not live here.
У глибокому вулику є мутяки. Вони ховаються, але вони є...
Danger lurks in every shadow, friends. But I protect you!
Do not think life in factory suit me.
Okay, we done? Go fight now.
